translate traditional_chinese episode004_0d0e70a4:


    c "我們怎麼做才能擺脫他？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_0c5bcd2a:


    c "我肯定你和蕾妮有充分理由逃離\"聖座\"。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_09b1766e:


    c "而且電話那頭的傢伙聽起來像個大混蛋。"


