translate traditional_chinese episode004_86e82c53:


    zi "是的，我或許能幫上忙。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_4d3f3918:


    c "怎麼個幫法？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_6eb9a580:


    zi "解決錢的問題。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_aef22107:


    c "接着說。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_43b9cb72:


    zi "但前提是你得同意一件事。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f33822ab:


    c "討價還價，基芙，真的嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d873cbf2:


    zi "只是爲我和蕾妮着想。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_b634b01b:


    c "我想這挺公平的。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_31f9375c:


    c "那麼，你想要什麼？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_945ca78f:


    zi "如果我告訴你的線索有結果了，我希望我們能在可預見的未來一直留在這艘船上。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_51e1a649:


    c "成交。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_87dcfd4a:


    zi "好。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_0656d340_1:


    zi "你聽說過圖布洛希人嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_27e906d1_1:


    c "聽過一點。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_59f09dd2_1:


    c "你是說那些頭腦簡單，四肢發達的怪物戰士，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_098a6543_1:


    zi "是的，一個高貴的星際戰士種族。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_261401c9_1:


    zi "榮譽對他們來說就是一切。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_7a62be60_1:


    zi "他們最後的偉大英雄，凱爾·塔沃特，是在著名的\"第五次榮耀之戰\"中死去的。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_9d733ca9_1:


    c "我想是些骯髒的星際種族屠殺，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cfe73b8a_1:


    zi "圖布洛希人戰後試圖回收陣亡戰士遺體，但塔沃特的遺體始終下落不明。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_3907883b_1:


    zi "但我知道他的遺體存放處。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_135bf551_1:


    c "所以這對圖布洛希人很值錢？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cfc9cd45_1:


    zi "無法爲近代史上最偉大的英雄舉行葬禮儀式，多年來始終是圖布洛希人的心頭刺。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_822bfb19_1:


    zi "這讓\"第五次榮耀之戰\"的戰績都蒙了塵。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d1d6cf5d:


    c "如果我們找到遺體物歸原主，他們就會感恩戴德？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f79996b0_1:


    zi "正是。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f1f42191_1:


    c "你能聯繫到圖布洛希人並與他們談判達成協議嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_babb6a60_1:


    zi "可以。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_19763502_2:


    c "很好，儘快聯絡。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_abc32c36_1:


    c "能把遺體位置告訴瑟琳嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_445f4b5e:


    zi "沒問題。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f2fbecf0:


    c "聽塞婭的意思...我們得拼命籌錢才行啊"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_b37c45b3:


    zi "聯絡後通知你。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_b18d974a:


    "我正和塞婭商討如何從塞特魯瓦處搞聚會邀請函，基芙突然走了進來。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_79237644:


    zi "聽說你們缺錢？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_56d0beb3:


    c "沒錯。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_200fa9bd:


    zi "我或許有辦法。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_aef22107_1:


    c "說來聽聽。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_43b9cb72_1:


    zi "但你要答應個條件。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f33822ab_1:


    c "基芙，這會兒討價還價，真的嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d873cbf2_1:


    zi "只是爲我和蕾妮着想。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_b634b01b_1:


    c "行吧。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_31f9375c_1:


    c "具體要什麼？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_945ca78f_1:


    zi "如果我告訴你的線索有結果了，我希望我們能在可預見的未來一直留在這艘船上。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_51e1a649_1:


    c "成交。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_87dcfd4a_1:


    zi "好。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_0656d340_2:


    zi "你聽說過圖布洛希人嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_27e906d1_2:


    c "知道一點。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_59f09dd2_2:


    c "你是說那些頭腦簡單，四肢發達的怪物戰士，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_098a6543_2:


    zi "是的，一個高貴的星際戰士種族。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_261401c9_2:


    zi "對他們來說，榮譽就是一切。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_7a62be60_2:


    zi "他們最後一個偉大的英雄，凱爾·塔沃特，在所謂的\"第五次榮耀之戰\"中犧牲了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_9d733ca9_2:


    c "一些混亂的星際種族滅絕，我猜？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cfe73b8a_2:


    zi "圖布洛希人試圖在戰後取回陣亡戰士的遺體，但塔沃特的遺體從未被找到。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_3907883b_2:


    zi "但我知道他的遺體被保存在哪兒。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_135bf551_2:


    c "這對圖布洛希人來說值很多錢？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cfc9cd45_2:


    zi "不能給他們近代史上最偉大的英雄之一進行最後的葬禮儀式，這是圖布洛希人多年來心頭的一根刺。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_822bfb19_2:


    zi "這讓\"第五次榮耀之戰\"的戰績都蒙了塵。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d1d6cf5d_1:


    c "如果我們找到遺體物歸原主，他們就會感恩戴德？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f79996b0_2:


    zi "正是。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f1f42191_2:


    c "你能聯繫到圖布洛希人並與他們談判達成協議嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_dac3fbaf:


    zi "我已經做過了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_29e33b2f:


    c "那太棒了！"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_45d16005:


    zi "我們將在指定地點帶着遺體見他們。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f6f4e970:


    zi "他們聽起來不太興奮，但圖布洛希人從不流露太多情緒。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_abc32c36_2:


    c "你能向瑟琳提供遺體應該在的地點嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_445f4b5e_1:


    zi "沒問題。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_e2f4aeb5:


    c "看起來我們需要所有能搞到的錢..."


translate traditional_chinese episode004_44966790:


    c "你已經和圖布洛希人談妥價碼了？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_0650ec46:


    zi "談妥了，成功交貨時付10萬信用點。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_8c2758b6:


    c "哇...{w} 他們可真稀罕那個叫塔沃特的傢伙，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_24dc949c:


    zi "主要是他們不願意把戰場上的英雄遺留在外。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d39e469d:


    c "問題是這筆錢夠不夠用啊，塞婭？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cbb358af:


    th "夠的，這筆錢應該能覆蓋前往塞特魯瓦的大部分開支，說不定能全包。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_83f9730b:


    c "好嘞，那我們出發吧。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_9f119176:


    zi "我和他們談過了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_45d16005_1:


    zi "我們得帶着遺體到指定地點和他們碰頭。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f6f4e970_1:


    zi "他們聽起來不激動，不過圖布洛希人從不輕易表露情緒。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_2218721d:


    c "價格談攏了嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_0650ec46_1:


    zi "談攏了，成功交貨時付10萬信用點。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_8c2758b6_1:


    c "哇...{w} 他們可真稀罕那個叫塔沃特的傢伙，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_24dc949c_1:


    zi "主要是他們不願意把戰場上的英雄遺留在外。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d39e469d_1:


    c "問題是這筆錢夠不夠用啊，塞婭？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cbb358af_1:


