    c "好嘞，那我們出發吧。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_a04589dd:


    "回到\"私生子\"號時，沒人對我遲到表示驚訝，估計基芙幫我編了藉口，真謝天謝地。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_364abfd4:


    "片刻後我們與圖布洛希飛船解除對接，再次啓程前往那顆行星——塞婭的接頭人將在那兒幫我們潛入拉尼莫·塞特魯瓦的宅邸。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_460039f9:


    c "我們具體去哪兒？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_8b544aef:


    th "巴蘭西斯星。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_2a298baf:


    c "陽光明媚的天堂？住滿了熱心幫忙的可愛居民？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_34d5208a:


    th "可惜不是。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cdc7890a:


    th "據我所知，那是個破敗不堪的垃圾地方。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_ebe08a5e:


    c "你從來沒去過那裡嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_9795b585:


    th "沒，但維特裏夫就住那裡。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_bfd9fd8d:


    c "我猜他就是那個會來幫我們的人吧？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_af9bf7b1:


    th "計劃就是這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_96aa7549:


    th "他關係網很廣，應該能幫我們搞到打動塞特魯瓦所需的證件。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_c9aa3d4a:


    "經過一番討價還價，我們才得以在巴蘭蘇拉——這顆行星上最大的城市——的衆多商業碼頭之一降落。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_2ddcb41d:


    "塞婭賄賂了一個港口官員，免掉了更多的停泊費和入場費，顯然這裡的制度就是這樣運作的。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_e8b6cc86:


    "其餘機組成員同意待在船上，這樣我和塞婭就能上街找她的朋友維特裏夫。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_076e9e11:


    "如果巴蘭蘇拉能作爲參考的話，她對巴蘭西斯星那'破敗不堪'的描述還真是相當客氣了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_2a877275:


    "這地方臭味燻天，街道兩旁堆積的垃圾山和頭頂繁忙空中交通的污染混合在一起。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_783788b1:


    "巴蘭蘇拉又擁擠又嘈雜，我實在想不通誰會自願住在這兒。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f268d9ab:


    c "這個傢伙，維特裏夫，他真喜歡住這兒？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_bd4607ec:


    th "不知道，但這裡有星系裡最好的幾個賭窩。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d2d1ce03:


    c "沒錯，這對某些人來說是個很能說服人的理由。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_41223e56:


    th "對維特裏夫來說，肯定是這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_cc8d5bd5:


    c "你有他的地址嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_6238cd05:


    th "有，離這兒不遠。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_8e31bf33:


    "一路街景一點也沒好轉，直到我們終於到了一幢巨大的公寓樓前。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_081bb5bd:


    c "挺溫馨的。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f0d31a6e:


    th "我打賭樓上的風景一定很美..."


translate traditional_chinese episode004_8839fe0a:


    "我們搭電梯上了十樓，一股尿味和發黴地毯的味道直衝鼻孔。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_63783d88:


    "走過一排長長的門，我們尋找着維特裏夫的房間號。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_45224ab5:


    "通過門前傳來的噪音判斷，大多數公寓似乎都有人住。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_f0ba3523:


    "維特裏夫的公寓在走廊的最盡頭，門口被幾個堆在一起的破漏的垃圾袋裝飾着。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_6d3701f9:


    "塞婭按了門邊的門鈴，我們等了一會兒然後又按了一次。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_7c8d94cf:


    c "他可能不在家？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_9fa09a46:


    "塞婭似乎不相信，用拳頭敲了敲門。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_b9b6a25a:


    "門嘎吱一聲開了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_fa88d347:


    c "糟糕..."


translate traditional_chinese episode004_d12fa3f5:


    th "操。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_fa60aa9d:


    th "這地方完全被搞亂了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_ea633aca:


    c "有維特裏夫的蹤跡嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_c0f2bf5e:


    th "我不確定，簡直一團亂糟糟的。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_4c8aac4a:


    th "可能我們該趕緊離開這鬼地方了？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_0efd7a85:


    c "不，他應該是我們通往塞特魯瓦的門票，看看裡面能不能找到線索吧。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_db909568:


    "公寓像是被人洗劫過，家具被翻倒，有些還壞了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_e99c7a60:


    "整個廚房裡的東西都被打碎倒在地上。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_9d9584c8:


    "除此之外，這地方空空如也，沒有維特裏夫的蹤影。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_411d0b64:


    "塞婭搜查了小臥室，但沒發現什麼值得注意的東西。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_a03098e1:


    c "這地方基本上空了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_00799241:


    th "看起來是這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_dca45d07:


    c "維特裏夫是個賭徒對吧，塞婭？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_ead6c963:


    th "是的，他是。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_dac0d395:


    c "那我們可能去幾個大賭場碰碰運氣，打聽他的消息？"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_ee9a83a9:


    "就在那一刻，我看到塞婭的眼睛瞪大，目光從我身後掃過。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_775f7765:


    th "[p_name], 小心！"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_01cab8f2:


    "很明顯，我們不再是公寓裡僅存的人了。"


translate traditional_chinese episode004_c81630a1:


    "幾秒鐘後，槍聲響徹我的耳朵。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_74599505:


    "基芙的坐標帶着我們穿過幾個跳躍門和恆星系統，才到達塔沃特遺體所在的星球。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_26857dbf:


    "當我們快進入行星軌道時，我讓基芙來艦橋上陪我。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_d8790acd:


    c "這地方會不會又是個鳥不拉屎的石頭星球？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_2f5ee769:


    zi "不，這是個鬱鬱蔥蔥的綠色星球。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_eef80a06:


    c "你以前來過這兒？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_88ac7e31:


    zi "我來過。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_65063668:


    c "等等，是你把遺體帶到這兒的？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7db8966d:


    zi "不可能，但我認識塔沃特的情人..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ead51403:


    zi "是她打完仗後把他帶到這兒的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_3e2639b3:


    c "所以你現在就讓我們去盜塔沃特的墓，這不是背叛朋友的信任嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_982e2ee4:


    zi "她不是我朋友。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_41fb7060:


    "瑟琳宣布我們快到了，打破了我和基芙之間的沉默。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_70ab8e7e:


    ce "準備降落，還有兩分鐘。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7db9c43e:


    c "她同意我們擺弄他的遺體？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_3aff339b:


    zi "老實說，我不在乎。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_4d34dd7f:


    zi "盧贊妮是我\"首領\"，但我恨她恨得牙痒痒。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_406d7af0:


    zi "我認識塔沃特的唯一原因是我們常來這兒，她讓我們去收集資源，而她自己跑到山裡去看他。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_0950a6bc:


    zi "有一天，好奇心佔了上風，我就跟在她後面，看她到底在搞什麼鬼。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_cc854e57:


    zi "我發現她在墳前祈禱。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9aa8c024:


    zi "她和塔沃特的短暫戀情是公開的祕密，但沒人知道\"第五次榮耀之戰\"結束時他出了什麼事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9738243e:


    zi "結果證明是他偷偷拋棄了隊伍，想跟盧贊妮在一起，打算叛逃..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_28203032:


    zi "他的運輸艇被一發激光炮的流彈打中，那就是她最後一次見到他。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_dbc888db:


    c "所以說，圖布洛希人眼中的光輝英雄..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_280bae60:


    zi "晚年全靠下半身思考，沒錯。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_89064838:


    c "猜猜看這事能讓圖布洛希人知道麼？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_dfd04fcb:


    zi "除非你不想要賞金了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a89de23b:


    c "盧贊妮後來怎麼了？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_d336fdc3:


    zi "她和塔沃特的戀情曝光後，挨了處分還被降職。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_8950bc9b:


    zi "那之後她在我這個層級就混不下去了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_890623ab:


    zi "當\"首領\"那會兒就夠差勁，連副手們都煩透她。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_c89a1dc8:


    zi "所以被揍過幾頓之後，人就徹底消失了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_27be0e5d:


    zi "說真的，沒半個人惦記她。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9a1de673:


    c "合着我們要找的就是個到處發情結果遭殃的貨，壓根不是什麼救英雄？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_849a0281:


    zi "故事大概就這麼回事，對。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_92678bef:


    c "行吧，只要圖布洛希人對着遺骨能滿意，我才懶得管這些..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_8c284c5f:


    zi "包他們滿意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_4df935e3:


    zi "塔沃特的名頭全靠\"第五次榮耀之戰\"的早些年撐着，那會兒還沒遇見盧贊妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_444259e7:


    c "他倆怎麼勾搭上的？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f23e3852:


    zi "盧贊妮帶的那個\"羣體\"駐紮在圖布洛希人剛攻佔的星球上。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_87c5f1eb:


    zi "說解放更恰當——那鬼地方原先就是個很骯髒的地方。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7634b3a4:


    c "\"羣體\"？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_4bcd3d85:


    c "慢着，你剛說\"首領\"和副手們來着...我才發現連你屬於哪個種族都不清楚。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_88a65849:


    zi "倫科伊族的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_c29b9dec:


    c "沒聽說過。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f199939e:


    zi "\"羣體\"就是倫科伊族人的生活單位，由\"首領\"管着。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_44f51600:


    zi "所有\"羣體\"合起來就是倫科伊族，歸我們\"倫科伊議會\"管。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e5efd927:


    c "所以這是一個種姓制度？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_690422a2:


    zi "在某種程度上，是的，等級森嚴。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_0bd943bf:


    c "但你不屬於一個\"羣體\"？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_2cce1644:


    zi "不，我現在不屬於任何\"羣體\"。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_db26f88f:


    zi "我有特殊許可。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_70ab8e7e_1:


    ce "準備在兩分鐘內着陸。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_fc2aee0b:


    "我和基芙的談話被\"私生子\"號進入大氣層打斷了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7eec8f24:


    "由於大氣幹擾，瑟琳無法將我們降落在靠近目標地點的地方，所以我們在一塊空地着陸，並決定由誰去尋找塔沃特的墳墓。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_17ce9ec9:


    "莉莉在經歷了牛獾獸的冒險後不久，沒心思再去探險了，但艾文對此完全沒問題。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_44f03721:


    "我們備足了補給和武器，然後就衝進了荒野。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_6e3df691:


    c "這似乎是個肥沃的星球，怎麼沒人住這兒？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_cc99a4fb:


    c "至少我在\"私生子\"號的電腦上沒看到任何城市或定居點。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9aaa64e4:


    zi "這是卡託爾人指定的一塊保護區星球，他們用這地方和其他星球來重新培育那些在他們自己母星上幾乎滅絕的野生動物。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_5583f43d:


    c "你應該早點告訴我們剛才降落在自然保護區裡的..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_665225eb:


    c "卡託爾人要多久才會來抓我們？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7ace9fd3:


    zi "卡託爾人..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_b737816a:


    c "誰在乎他們？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_185c84ed:


    c "卡託爾人多久才會發現我們正在破壞他們一個自然保護區的寧靜？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_335961ae:


    zi "別擔心，這些保護區監管不嚴，我們一天內就會離開這裡。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_c1bfa14d:


    c "既然你這麼說了..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_22b5ffdd:


    "我們走了幾個小時，基芙大部分路途都帶路。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ee335bc5:


    "到了一個小泉水邊，艾文突然停了下來。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_1b796d93:


    av "別動！"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_297d93f3:


    c "怎麼了？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_38a1d53b:


    av "陷阱。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a9897648:


    c "基芙，你不是說這星球沒人居住嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_225573d6:


    zi "應該是...{w} 本該如此的..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_24c80ce2:


    zi "或許是老舊的陷阱？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_bbc642ef:


    av "可能吧..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_058b1389:


    c "你能拆掉它嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_82cb0616:


    av "也許能。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_16686f1d:


    "直到艾文用樹枝戳中前，我完全沒發現高草叢裡的陷阱。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_65d97131:


    "這是個簡陋裝置，獵人常用，踩中會疼得要命。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_6e1b63ea:


    "她戳動觸發機關，陷阱啪地夾緊後，才示意我們繼續前進。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_34ddfaf7:


    av "接下來必須加倍小心，這不用多說了吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_dab747e7:


    av "跟緊我身後。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f20b586a:


    "我們行進速度明顯放慢，艾文又拆除了三個類似的裝置。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_743ad46d:


    zi "快到了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_116a5347:


    c "很好，千萬小心，設陷阱的傢伙可能還藏着後手。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_527628c2:


    c "基芙你皺眉了，怎麼回事？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_32dfda68:


    zi "按說就是這個位置..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_16c44aec:


    c "這話聽着不妙。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ae27fe57:


    zi "不，我確定。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e094f7d2:


    zi "這就是他墓地的位置，我曾看見她在這裡祈禱。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_4933f015:


    av "但現在根本看不見墳墓。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_2c0ba39b:


    av "也許是標記被毀了？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_3684967b:


    c "恐怕是被討厭訪客的傢伙破壞了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a46ba6a8:


    c "要試着挖挖看嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_c528ebe3:


    zi "但——"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ff47e320:


    "一聲金屬敲擊打斷了基芙，一個石塊大小的物體被扔在我們中間。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_71ee5425:


    av "手榴彈！"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_4f8cd348:


    "我們還沒來得及跳開，裝置就發出一聲響亮的咔嗒聲爆開，我們全被籠罩在了一團氣體中。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a1d188cb:


    "當我們癱倒在地上咳嗽時，一個戴着防毒面具的身影穿過煙霧走了出來。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_8fbcfe58:


    lu "...好的，親愛的，我們會的，很快。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_1f16e87e:


    lu "有闖入者，我已經處理掉了他們。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7266e7a7:


    lu "其實，他們也許能派上用場..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_8f367d31:


    "一個女人對着骷髏發出哄哄聲可絕對不是我被氣體燻倒後想象的那種景象。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a6cb856b:


    "但她就在那兒，在祭壇前喃喃自語。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_87774100:


    "不管怎樣，我們找到了塔沃特，但現在我們被繩子捆了起來，這就讓事情複雜多了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_b4a91900:


    c "艾文？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_d94a343f:


    c "基芙？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_615277dd:


    lu "啊，你醒了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_470987e5:


    lu "不，別裝着你還沒醒，我聽見你低聲說話了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_483f1786:


    c "好吧，你抓到我了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_6051bfe8:


    c "我現在想被鬆綁了，拜託。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_3ed75f72:


    lu "抱歉，但那不可能。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_6cda98d1:


    c "你看起來像極了基芙..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a7aba751:


    c "靠，你是塔沃特的情人吧，不是嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_d017f41e:


    lu "是的，我是盧贊妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_0541f5f2:


    c "媽的，你是盧贊妮吧，不是嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9e146380:


    lu "是的，基芙告訴過你我的事嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_26eefe0a:


    c "是的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_5b3cda73:


    c "顯然，只有好話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_5cf8d2bc:


    lu "人類，你撒謊可真輕鬆。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9c64475c:


    lu "基芙是來找我的嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7385c558:


    lu "終於要報仇了？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e69e42b8:


    c "不。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_c876bc0a:


    lu "那你爲什麼在這裡？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_140d9e92:


    c "我們是來找塔沃特的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_aeb3fcc2:


    lu "是嘛。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_2d062e9d:


    lu "基芙不能讓過去的事情都算了，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_97ca0b98:


    c "我想不是。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_26eefe0a_1:


    c "是的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_21cdb719:


    lu "我就知道她不能讓我走。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ebb88060:


    lu "嫉妒的婊子。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_0fba8060:


    c "嫉妒？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_33d2369a:


    lu "啊，所以她沒告訴你一切？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_c340eda9:


    lu "基芙和我...{w} 我們互相有好感。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_b5e9cf77:


    lu "但那都是任性，是我在經歷真愛時才意識到的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e966bd6d:


    c "爲了塔沃特？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e6ec6214:


    lu "是的，爲了他。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_1a138408:


    lu "基芙無法忍受我們在一起的想法，所以當我倒大黴時她高興得要死。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f1b4d203:


    lu "我懷疑她甚至還插了一手。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f4747fdb:


    zi "盧贊妮？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_615277dd_1:


    lu "啊，你醒了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_938c90ca:


    lu "我沒想到我會再見到你。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_b2eed2c5:


    zi "我也沒想到。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ce3c039a:


    lu "所以你是來玷污我愛人墳墓的？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_cd1ac618:


    zi "這是你說的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_b59019d4:


    zi "我只是來給他辦個正經葬禮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_4b8df964:


    lu "你憑什麼這麼做？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9b1441fb:


    lu "塔沃特是我的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_760ec26c:


    zi "塔沃特已經死了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_59918481:


    lu "那爲什麼他的靈魂還在跟我說話，基芙？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_57c1254e:


    lu "不，我的愛人還在這裡徘徊，渴望重獲新生。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a7dd4237:


    c "就問一嘴，圖布洛希人真能轉世還是怎麼着，基芙？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e87f1abb:


    zi "不，他們不能。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f5f7c27d:


    c "好吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e0ca4bf0:


    lu "得了吧基芙，你對《恩柯伊·凱爾賈爾靈界論著》的了解不比我少。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f6ca2a94:


    zi "是，我知道那就是瘋子異教徒的胡言亂語，早該被世人遺忘。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_97d9436a:


    lu "等我完成儀式，你跟我說話的態度就該變了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_39ed0d00:


    lu "總之你來得正是時候，說不定是冥冥之中的預示。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_98a55464:


    c "儀式？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_81189999:


    lu "沒錯，正好拿你們其中一個當容器，把塔沃特的靈魂接回人世。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_20104b6e:


    zi "盧贊妮，你不可能真打算實施凱爾賈爾寫的那些儀式。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_841edc8a:


    c "什麼儀式？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_476befb3:


    lu "這是唯一的辦法。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_547e2343:


    zi "你瘋了，盧贊妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_7f19607c:


    lu "等着瞧吧基芙，我會證明你錯了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a474d3f7:


    lu "這小子看着就是儀式的首選容器。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_bf154317:


    c "等等，什麼?!"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_fe678059:


    lu "安靜！我需要準備。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_644ff386:


    "她背向我們，盧贊妮開始在石壇和周圍的表面上擺放水晶。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_26ab546f:


    c "基芙，她在說什麼儀式啊？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f4438140:


    zi "一本丟臉的前議員寫的舊書裏的迷信胡話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_1773eeac:


    zi "它描述了所謂的靈界的存在，還有跟那裡居民交流的辦法。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e62309ca:


    zi "凱爾賈爾也談到通過舉行儀式與靈體結合來操控它們。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_eb72113d:


    c "真有意思，但我到底會發生什麼？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_48b3c5e9:


    zi "你會和她做愛，等你爽到極點時，她就會往你心上捅一刀。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_a54110fd:


    zi "你血流不止時，她會念起那套規定咒語，據說就能讓塔沃特還魂。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_330f526e:


    c "老實說，高潮那部分之後我就沒聽懂..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_b437b351:


    c "操。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_75021404:


    zi "我建議你儘量堅持久一點。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_1ffd2873:


    c "哎呀，多謝你這條寶貴建議..."


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_08648795:


    c "要是艾文醒了該多好！"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_ec1114b3:


    av "我醒了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_1e3eb9f2:


    av "而且，我的手腕繩子都快割斷了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_9d858297:


    c "你爲什麼不吭聲？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_e005e626:


    av "不想驚動盧贊妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_f48bcb95:


    c "我們該怎麼辦？"


translate traditional_chinese ep004_skarak_deec1264:


